---
// Hero section - "THE EDITORIAL"
---
<section class="hero" id="inicio" aria-label="Bienvenida al restaurante The Editorial">
  <div class="hero__bg">
    <img
      src="/hero.png"
      alt="Alta cocina mediterránea en Madrid – plato elaborado con ingredientes frescos del Mediterráneo"
      class="hero__img"
      fetchpriority="high"
      width="1920"
      height="1080"
    />
    <div class="hero__overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero__content container">
    <p class="label-lg hero__label animate-fade-up gold">Madrid · Barrio de Salamanca · Desde 1984</p>

    <h1 class="display-lg hero__title animate-fade-up delay-1">
      Auténtica cocina<br />
      <span class="italic">mediterránea</span><br />
      en Madrid
    </h1>

    <p class="body-lg hero__subtitle animate-fade-up delay-2">
      Tradición, calidad y sabor en cada plato. Un viaje sensorial<br class="hide-mobile" />
      por las costas del Mediterráneo sin salir del corazón de la capital.
    </p>

    <div class="hero__actions animate-fade-up delay-3">
      <a href="#reservas" class="btn-primary" id="hero-reserve-btn">Reservar mesa</a>
      <a href="#carta" class="btn-ghost" id="hero-menu-btn">Ver carta</a>
    </div>

    <div class="hero__badge animate-fade-up delay-4" aria-label="Desde 1984, legado de excelencia culinaria en Madrid">
      <span class="label-md muted">1984</span>
      <p class="body-md">Legado de excelencia<br/>culinaria en Madrid</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    padding-bottom: var(--sp-20);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero__bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
  }

  .hero__img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 20%;
    filter: grayscale(25%);
  }

  .hero__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, transparent 10%, rgba(0,0,0,0.35) 60%),
                linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.82) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.3) 50%, transparent 100%);
  }

  .hero__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    color: #f0f1f1;
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--sp-6);
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .hero__label {
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }

  .hero__title {
    color: var(--inverse-on-surface);
  }

  .hero__subtitle {
    color: rgba(240, 241, 241, 0.78);
    max-width: 540px;
  }

  .hero__actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--sp-4);
  }

  .hero__actions .btn-ghost {
    color: var(--inverse-on-surface);
    border-color: rgba(240,241,241,0.4);
  }

  .hero__actions .btn-ghost:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-color: rgba(240,241,241,0.8);
  }

  .hero__badge {
    margin-top: var(--sp-8);
    padding-top: var(--sp-6);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(240,241,241,0.15);
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--sp-1);
  }

  .hero__badge .muted {
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }

  .hero__badge p {
    color: rgba(240,241,241,0.6);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero__content {
      padding-bottom: var(--sp-4);
    }
  }

  .hide-mobile {
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hide-mobile { display: block; }
  }
</style>
